Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:41.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}即便已然伤痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:44.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}走り続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:44.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}我依然继续前行
